body:
# RU
[COF (Create-Origins-Farmer's Delight)](https://modrinth.com/modpack/cof/) - это модпак, включающий в себя самые популярные и в каком-то смысле легендарные моды нынешнего времени, множество оптимизации, а также добавляющий совместимость, в связке с множеством аддонов к ним.
# ENG
[COF (Create-Origins-Farmer's Delight)](https://modrinth.com/modpack/cof/) is a modpack that includes the most popular and in some sense legendary mods of the present time, a lot of optimization, as well as adding compatibility, in conjunction with a variety of addons to them.
## Основные Моды (Main Mods):
- #### [Create Fabric](https://modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric-sodium-fix)
   -  Create: Slice & Dice;
   -  Create: Origins;
   -  Create: New Age;
   -  Create: Ore Excavation;
   -  Create: Steam 'n' Rails;
   - ...
- #### [Farmer's Delight](https://modrinth.com/mod/farmers-delight-fabric)
   -  Create: Slice & Dice;
   -  Fabric Seasons: Delight Compact;
   -  Farmer's Respite;
   -  Expanded Delight;
   - ...
- #### [Origins](https://modrinth.com/mod/origins)
   -  Origins: Extra
   -  Origins: Classes
   -  Create: Origins
